name: gccsa_w12a_ind_of_emp_by_occ_census_2016
title: GCCSA-W12a Industry of Employment by Occupation-Census 2016

legal.licenceType: Creative Commons Attribution 2.5 Australia (CC BY 2.5 AU)

abstract:
GCCSA based data for Industry of Employment by Occupation, in Working Population Profile (WPP), 2016 Census. Count of employed persons aged 15 years and over. W12 is broken up into 2 sections (W12a - W12b), this section contains 'Agriculture forestry and fishing Managers' - 'Inadequately described Not stated Total'. The data is by GCCSA 2016 boundaries. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
Note: There are small random adjustments made to all cell values to protect the confidentiality of data. These adjustments may cause the sum of rows or columns to differ by small amounts from table totals.
For more information visit the data source: http://www.abs.gov.au/census.
